@%:@! /bin/sh
@%:@ Guess values for system-dependent variables and create Makefiles.
@%:@ Generated by GNU Autoconf 2.59 for acro VOTD.
@%:@
@%:@ Report bugs to <acro-help@software.sandia.gov>.
